ABOUT US
      With a heritage dating back to 1872, Great American Life® has a long history of helping people achieve their financial goals. We are a top five provider of fixed and fixed-indexed annuities in the financial institution market, and we continue to evolve our product portfolio as the marketplace and consumer needs change. We are a member of Great American Insurance Group and a subsidiary of American Financial Group, Inc. (AFG), which is publicly traded on the New York Stock Exchange (NYSE:AFG).



FINANCIAL STRENGTH
      Take comfort knowing you’ve partnered with a company that has undeniable financial strength. Great American Life has been rated A or higher by A.M. Best for more than 30 consecutive years. We are currently rated “A+” by Standard & Poor’s and “A (Excellent)” by A.M. Best. Refer to our Financial Strength brochure to learn more.
S&P rating affirmed Feb. 8, 2017. A.M. Best rating affirmed May 12, 2016.








